CustomField.description: Defines the Mapquest Endpoint URL used to validate against the endpoint in Salesforce remote site settings before using the Mapquest Geolocation API. This URL should be a subset of the Geolocation Service URL.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Defines the Mapquest Endpoint URL used to validate against the endpoint in Salesforce remote site settings before using the Mapquest Geolocation API. This URL should be a subset of the Geolocation Service URL.
CustomField.label: Mapquest Endpoint URL
